@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@targetUserId = 2
@missingUserId = 999999
@invalidUserId = 0

### 提示：正常修改会写入数据库；如需对照初始种子数据，请先重置 db/seeds/001_demo_data.sql

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：修改用户状态为禁用
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2
}

### 正常路径：修改用户状态为启用
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录修改用户状态，预期 401
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2
}

### 异常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工修改用户状态，预期 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2
}

### 异常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：user_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{invalidUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2
}

### 异常路径：缺少 status，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：status 不是整数，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "disabled"
}

### 异常路径：status 不在枚举范围内，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{targetUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 3
}

### 异常路径：用户不存在，预期 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{missingUserId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2
}
